### EXERCISE 3.5 & 3.6: CREATE NEW PERSON - SUCCESS
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jan Nowak",
  "number": "555-666-7777"
}

###

### EXERCISE 3.6: ERROR - MISSING NUMBER
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Kowalska"
}

###

### EXERCISE 3.6: ERROR - MISSING NAME
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "111-222-3333"
}

###

### EXERCISE 3.6: ERROR - DUPLICATE NAME
